description: If you play Fun Fair Positive Soccer, this skill will look up your next game time for a spoken league and team number.  You simply start by saying "Alexa, open fun fair games".  If she knows your league from a previous lookup, she will just ask your team number, otherwise you will need to give her your league name.  If you need to look up another team number, for example, just say "Alexa, when is my next game for team 101".  If you need to change the league she remembered, just "change league".
name: Fun Fair Positive Soccer
shortDescription: Find out your next Fun Fair Positive Soccer game time.
